{"tid":2047594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【金融制裁應該仲要等一等】美國政府標售壽山村道37號物業　7月底截標","createTime":"2020-06-02T08:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T08:46:11.000Z","uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ea252bdc0266b1f4fdbf5550a2333a4cdbe886e8","tid":2047594,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T08:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200602/photo/bkn-20200602141139150-0602_00842_001_01p.jpg?20200602145850\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200602%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200602141139150-0602_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20200602145850&h=3ffccd7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世邦魏理仕獲業主委任為獨家代理，公開招標出售香港壽臣山壽山村道37號物業。物業由美國政府於1948年購入，並持有至今作美國駐港領事館宿舍之用，現作公開招標出售，截標日期為7月31日(星期五)正午。<br />\n<br />\n該物業於1983年落成，現為6幢低密度住宅物業，提供26個單位及52個車位，另設室外游泳池。物業具重建潛力，地盤面積約94,796方呎，可重建面積約47,397方呎。地盤佈局修長，將可重建為海景豪宅獨立屋項目，日後買家亦可為每幢獨立屋設獨立門號。<br />\n<br />\n世邦魏理仕香港資本市場部資深董事王國偉稱，物業之地契限制有別於南區傳統舊屋契，發展商毋須補地價已可興建多間獨立屋，可省去補地價的支出及時間成本。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，毗鄰物業為壽山村道39號，於2018年6月由中資華潤置地(01109)以59.29億港元購入，每方呎樓面地價85,847元。<br />\n<br />\nsource : <a href=\"http://ON.CC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FON.CC&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbZNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=3719f4ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ON.CC</a>"},{"pid":"9dc4dae67b03400fc87175e12e7c9fea87e4631f","tid":2047594,"uid":54386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"並持有至今作美國駐港領事館宿舍之用<br />\n之後搬離香港定搵左地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22eed87d0123f7d11cf2488aba73b78df2cb177","tid":2047594,"uid":52594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T08:16:19.000Z","msg":"7 月底前安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d54a1a0316b7969a592b60ad2b7870a3cc1e5e","tid":2047594,"uid":164266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"物業於48年購入，但係83年落成？"},{"pid":"4498c4f4a427c21779c751320b23121a659f4e72","tid":2047594,"uid":8257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a6d54a1a0316b7969a592b60ad2b7870a3cc1e5e","tid":2047594,"uid":164266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"物業於48年購入，但係83年落成？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T08:46:11.000Z","msg":"重建<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}